    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting with my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, it\u2019s a total gem. This beauty is in truly incredible shape\u2014it looks and drives just like it did the day it left the showroom! I\u2019ve been super meticulous about maintenance and keeping it garage-stored, so it\u2019s basically spotless inside and out. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s been pampered and is ready to hit the road without a single worry, this is the one for you. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 47250.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
