      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 4
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 2002 BMW M3 (E46) is a concours-level specimen featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies and high-pressure Double VANOS variable valve timing. Power is managed via a precise 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a variable M-differential lock. The chassis is impeccably preserved with no subframe fatigue, and the suspension retains factory-spec bushings and dampening rates. Finished in Carbon Black over Nappa leather, the finish is devoid of swirling or oxidation. Mechanically, the rod bearing service and VANOS hub reinforcements have been completed, ensuring the 8,000 RPM valvetrain operates with surgical precision. A turn-key investment for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 4
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Mint condition. Flawless exterior. Pristine interior. Zero mechanical issues. Clean title in hand.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
