    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true time capsule, presented in absolute showroom condition. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like finish with zero chips, scratches, or swirls, while the factory wheels are entirely free of curb rash. Inside, the cabin remains in a factory-fresh state; the premium leather is supple with no bolster wear, and every electronic component functions perfectly. Meticulously maintained with a documented service history and always garage-kept under a breathable cover, this car drives exactly as it did the day it left the dealership. It is a rare find for a discerning buyer seeking a vehicle that looks and feels brand new.",
      "price": 48500.0,
